title: BRIEF-Velto Cars sees FY 2015 net profit of 4 mln zlotys
text:
BRIEF-Velto Cars sees FY 2015 net profit of 4 mln zlotys Sept 29 
Sept 29 Velto Cars SA : 
* Sees FY 2015 revenue of 25 million zlotys ($6.6 million) 
* Sees FY 2015 net profit of 4 million zlotys Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 3.7808 zlotys) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
